    <h1>Historical Context: Jewish Boryslaw</h1>
    <p>Information compiled from Yad Vashem's <em>Pinkas HaKehillot</em> (Encyclopedia of Jewish Communities in Poland), a record of Jewish communal life in pre-war Eastern Europe.</p>

    <!-- Key facts callout -->
